Not fewer than three persons have been arrested for ritual money-making in Katsina State. <img class="size-medium wp-image-1263671 aligncenter" src="https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Katsina.jpg?resize=300%2C233&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="300" height="233" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Katsina.jpg?resize=300%2C233&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Katsina.jpg?resize=768%2C597&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Katsina.jpg?resize=1024%2C797&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Katsina.jpg?resize=58%2C45&amp;ssl=1 58w, https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Katsina.jpg?resize=249%2C194&amp;ssl=1 249w, https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Katsina.jpg?resize=167%2C130&amp;ssl=1 167w, https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Katsina.jpg?resize=560%2C436&amp;ssl=1 560w, https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Katsina.jpg?w=1234&amp;ssl=1 1234w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Spokesperson of the Katsina State Police Command, ASP Anas A Gezawa said the trio were arrested after duping one Mr Chinedu Onojo with the intent of doubling his money by rituals means. Gezawa confirmed the development while parading the members of the syndicate who specialise in criminal conspiracy and obtaining money by false pretence. According to him, “On 10/10/2019 base on a tip off, the command succeeded in arresting a syndicate that specialises in criminal conspiracy and obtaining money by false pretence. “During the cause of preliminary investigation, it revealed that the trio conspired and duped one Mr Chinedu Onojo ‘M’ of Sabon layi quarters katsina quarters the sum of 94.000.00 with the intent of doubling his money by rituals means. The said complainer quickly comprehend their antecedents and promptly reported the issue to the police. ⤕VIDEO: Why I stopped being Fatoyinbo’s spiritual father 5 years ago ― Pastor Oset ⤕I killed 16 of my victims, offered their blood for ritual — kidnap kingpin “SARS operatives of the command expeditiously swung into action and arrested the following culprits: Ayemguda Dada ‘m’ 32 years, Ogunmoroti Ojo ‘m’ 21 years and Ogidpe Akin ‘m’ 22 years, all of Ijebu Ode of Ogun state,” Gezawa said. The Police Public Relations Officer said it recovered from the gang exhibits such as 50 Pieces of counterfeits 100 US dollers note, 11 pieces of counterfeits 1 US dollars note and 3 sets of different type of handsets. Other exhibits include 1 drum covers with black materials with charms objects, calabash containing palm oi with salts added with some incriminating objects, 2 wooden gods and 3 white pigeons 1 alive and some other incriminating objects. ASP Gezawa, however, said the case is under discreet investigations. Vanguard News Nigeria. The Police Command in Anambra said it had arrested 95 suspected cultists and three suspected members of an armed robbery syndicate in the state. May 12, 2019 In "News" The Osun State Police Command Wedndesday paraded two people suspected to be realists who specialize in duping and defrauding unsuspecting members of the public under the pretence of being herbalists. October 11, 2017 In "News" KATSINA - It was a breakthrough for the Nigeria Police Force and the Nigeria Immigration service, Katsina State Commands as the duo recorded series of arrests of criminals recently in the state August 18, 2018 In "News"